txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Glossy essence from the shades north-west of Amon Raith. Deliver the items to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith.
'I am certain that the Elf will be pleased with this collection. Thank you.'
'That Elf, Londrandir, asked for two things, dust and essence both from the shades to north-west. Who am I to argue? I am just organizing the collection.'
Rangers of Esteld√≠n Task: Glossy Essence
Nathan Hodges, at Amon Raith, awaits the collection and delivery of glossy essence.
Deliver the glossy essence to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith
You have accepted a task to deliver glossy essence to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith in the North Downs. You can find glossy essence on shades north-west of Amon Raith.
Wanted: Glossy essence from the shades north-west of Amon Raith.
